{"tid":160202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國毒霧有幾可怕？一年致300萬人早死！！","createTime":"2017-03-17T13:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T17:03:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca27525234ee2b3bb514bf2774ace2b932293139","tid":160202,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:56:29.000Z","msg":"毒霧肆虐 中國每年300萬人早死<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/17/215321_043e0429ea3e672467d315188be5b9f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2F215321_043e0429ea3e672467d315188be5b9f4.jpg&h=818ecd17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國研究人員在英國醫學雜誌（BMJ）發表調查報告（點擊看全文）指出，中國政府倘能治理好空氣污染、解決毒霧問題，每年可以挽救300萬人的生命，讓他們免於早死。<br />\n<br />\n中國疾病控制與預防中心的研究人員，比較了38個中國最大城市的顆粒物空氣污染水平，得出的結論是，空氣污染可以引發嚴重呼吸道疾、病導致過早死亡。其中，空氣污染可誘發哮喘和慢性阻塞性肺疾病（COPD），增加猝死風險。<br />\n<br />\n【延伸閱讀】陸網民KUSO拍「舌尖上的毒霧」 笑中有淚（有片）<br />\n<br />\n【延伸閱讀】大媽毋懼毒霧跳廣場舞 如現實版《陰屍路》（有片）<br />\n<br />\n【延伸閱讀】李總承諾「藍天不變奢侈品」 環保股聞風起動<br />\n<br />\n據了解，研究報告追蹤38個城市的每天空氣污染數據，涉及範圍覆蓋超過兩億人口；結果推論，上述城市從2010年1月至2013年6月期間，有約35萬人因空氣污染而死亡。<br />\n<br />\n中國研究人員在38城調查<br />\n<br />\n研究人員再通過對這35萬死亡病例的分析，發現超標的空氣污染物，使每天死亡人數增加了0.44％。當中空氣懸浮粒子PM10的污染，對婦女和60歲以上老人的危害更大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1710000/1710620/cns20170104029_630_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1710000%2F1710620%2Fcns20170104029_630_1024.jpg&h=b2332392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中國政府如果能夠治理好空氣污染，據稱每年可以挽救300萬人的生命。</span><br />\n<br />\nPM10即直徑小於10微米粒子，主要來自工業和汽車排放。調查報告說，這類小的顆粒是特別危險的，因它們可以粘在呼吸道裏，對人體健康的損害是長久性的。<br />\n<br />\n研究報告以上述38城市的死亡數字為基礎，按照中國13.3億人口來估算，如果將空氣污染降低到世界衛生組織建議的標準，每年可防止300萬人過早死亡。<br />\n<br />\nPM10對人體危害巨大<br />\n<br />\n調查還指出，這個平均數字是針對38個樣辦城市的研究粗略評估而得，而中國農村的污染可能更嚴重，對中國農村污染的研究目前仍然是空白。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員建議，如果中國能夠採納和實施嚴格的空氣質量標準的話， 將大大有利於公眾健康。"},{"pid":"e4a254bb4a7d40d6d90d967573f2a0bc73f35305","tid":160202,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:58:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://china.hket.com/article/1710620?r=mcsdfb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1710620%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb2&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d08f3c78\" target=\"_blank\">http://china.hket.com/article/1710620?r=mcsdfb2</a>"},{"pid":"41a01dff066095a3d5de690579ec7f9abc6eed2e","tid":160202,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:58:32.000Z","msg":"得三百萬會唔會太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f9d9bde3469882683d8a4931cc8f299aa75acc","tid":160202,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T13:58:50.000Z","msg":"根本係想減少中老年人口"},{"pid":"9a0b567a8b02ca3029184ffe2bb2eac62683a9b2","tid":160202,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本係想減少中老年人口</blockquote>無撚有錯<br />\n一年多300萬人仲得了！？"},{"pid":"38c19ae08eef1802fa71d4a466ddbe3abed41751","tid":160202,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"之前ISIS 仲話要襲擊中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你ISIS 殺到手軟, 都無中共一年殺既中國人1/10 咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9980ed8796e17760126b55de569da1bd0f01eece","tid":160202,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133553067fbeca747db1c29376897358323d5df0","tid":160202,"uid":27055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4ebbd3afb16d10a026da41f9dabf7a2e12d501","tid":160202,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8020c0aa3e88f878118e03fac765e7da14cae05","tid":160202,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5e27345e98c19ed0d6349f07455b3175a80b20","tid":160202,"uid":73748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:55:41.000Z","msg":"中國會死人？"},{"pid":"ffc4cb9eae561eff3a9e7c9d018ab60509a1bfd3","tid":160202,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"支那繁殖率勁過小強<br />\n死1個生10個<br />\n300萬真係濕濕碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f81a7ec4dac09390818996d1d6e0db014da20a","tid":160202,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:22:19.000Z","msg":"死多2個0仲好"},{"pid":"54303a51a3d5749b43fe1cef21f4e582a841d186","tid":160202,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:25:58.000Z","msg":"降低人口老化，廢老死清光"},{"pid":"d071b943a64c35e5c6b768fcc1788da795d7bd54","tid":160202,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:53:19.000Z","msg":"300萬太少"},{"pid":"65b6aa7191baa99bea0bed0e2fb214f87f76b4b8","tid":160202,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"3億就幾好"},{"pid":"de162e8ce964b814ad10deacad7ef6a736a456aa","tid":160202,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:03:39.000Z","msg":"速度有啲慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}